00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:43,360
First, let's take a look at their relationship.

295
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,410
Socrates

296
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:46,350
was Plato's teacher,

297
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:49,050
