298
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:50,890
[Socrates Plato Aristotle Teacher Teacher]

299
00:15:50,980 --> 00:15:54,350
It is said that Socrates liked to initiate arguments with various people

300
00:15:54,350 --> 00:15:57,420
