301
00:15:57,420 --> 00:16:01,250
If we compare him to a contemporary figure, he's quite like Mr. Hiroyuki.

302
00:16:01,250 --> 00:16:02,970
They're pretty alike.

303
00:16:06,580 --> 00:16:08,230
By the way,

304
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:10,090
Socrates and Plato

305
00:16:10,110 --> 00:16:12,270
